title: Healthcare Leaders, NVIDIA CEO Share AI Innovation Across the Industry
content:
AI is making inroads across the entire healthcare industry — from genomic research to drug discovery, clinical trial workflows and patient care. In a fireside chat Monday during the annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference in San Francisco, NVIDIA founder and CEO Jensen Huang took the stage with industry leaders progressing each of these areas to	
		Read Article
author: Isha Salian
